description: Jack needs to find at least 80 shrimps and 50 conches to pay his monthly rent for his beach house . There are two beaches that Jack frequents : Silver Beach and Lucent Beach . Each day at Silver beach , Jack finds 7 shrimps and 3 conches . Each day at Lucent Beach , Jack finds 4 shrimps and 6 conches . Formulate an LP to help Jack meet his requirements while spending a minimal amount of time .
